-- Monte Paschi Says Press Reports on Need for Capital Boost Are `Unfounded'
-- Sonia Sirletti
-- 2010-07-02T11:25:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-02/monte-paschi-says-press-reports-on-need-for-capital-boost-are-unfounded-.html

          
          
             Banca Monte dei Paschi di Siena SpA
said reports of the bank’s need to boost capital are
“unfounded,” according to an e-mailed statement.  
 Capital ratios are “more than adequate,” the company
said.  
          
          


  


        